OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWednesday generally dry and
OL,6,Fbright, with some sunny spells likely
OL,7,Facross the region. Light winds
OL,8,Ffreshening a little and feeling warm
OL,9,Fby afternoon, with highest
OL,10,Ftemperatures towards the east of the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying mostly dry and mild
OL,14,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,15,Fcloud and some clearer spells. Chance
OL,16,Fof patchy light rain across some north-
OL,17,Fwestern areas after midnight. Winds
OL,18,Ffreshening a little.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
