OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FThursday again mainly fine
OL,6,Fwith some bright or sunny spells. Any
OL,7,Fpatchy rain or showers clearing south-
OL,8,Feastwards by late morning. Breezy by
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,12,Fand into the weekend likely to remain
OL,13,Fdry and occasionally breezy, with some
OL,14,Fclear or sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,15,Fmostly above average throughout.
